@Comment:	Time is 0:05
@Comment:	Chi is a pretty good reader who seems to read words rather than phrases. Mot asks Chi to point to the leaf. Duh! Sounds out through carefully each time but always gets it. May be using contextual cues , because reads text supported by pictures more fluidly. But still reads other stuff well. Stumbles on stomach but insists on figuring it out herself and does. When Chi reads left instead of felt Mot asks where it says felt and Chi figures out the error herself.
